{"tid":439181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實fg 黎講有個好上司真係好重要","createTime":"2017-10-17T14:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T15:03:55.000Z","uid":119485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b62652b9a77b94d6228d7e78e42cc32924c858d","tid":439181,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"同一公司跟唔同上司真係唔同世界 <br />\n<br />\n我返緊間公司算中型大概二/三十人<br />\nInterview 係CEO 同 個女manager In 我<br />\nWeek 1 個manager 咩都無教我<br />\n淨係比少少report 我試下做<br />\n其餘時間叫我睇舊file <br />\n<br />\n之後隔左幾日 CEO 同manager 叫我入房<br />\n個manager 話我唔適合份工<br />\n我心諗又唔教我野 又唔比野我做 我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩個CEO 幾鐘意我 叫我試下跟第二個manager <br />\n換左個manager （男三十幾歲少少毒）工作環境真係唔同曬<br />\n好肯教我（ 因為教完推曬比我做）<br />\n每日叫我準時收工 <br />\n返9-5:30 佢5:25 已經ready 帶我地一齊出去打卡<br />\n另外成日同我講做又36 唔做又36 唔洗咁博 <br />\n<br />\n三個月之後我順利過左試用<br />\n老闆重話我OK 加埋人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以千奇 千奇唔好跟女上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26db619b18edc2029d43ea439cc7ff05d758ebba","tid":439181,"uid":100303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"都唔係嘅 我個女上司好好 男上司好賤 所以睇人啦"},{"pid":"544b40b2fc73b35615f06cdc0b52e689d2bad5a4","tid":439181,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac933a6fff40bde7d6d0d8378723a9f0bbff9f73","tid":439181,"uid":32722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:47:33.000Z","msg":"仔跟女上屍，女跟男上屍係比較好"},{"pid":"6ce448dc13ee83c2df454f298a721fd966cf8f55","tid":439181,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}